Enum Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Location>
      • project1.Location
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Location>
    public enum Location
extends java.lang.Enum<Location>
    This class contains a fixed set of possible locations with the instance attributes consisting of zipCode and cityName and methods that retrieve these attributes and compare Location objects.
    Author:
    Darrel Dsouza, Anton Derkach
